458
00:25:13.099 --> 00:25:14.317
Much better. thank you.

459
00:25:14.448 --> 00:25:16.319
Good. Uh. did Kristi
figure out what happened?

460
00:25:16.450 --> 00:25:19.279
Not yet. It's...

461
00:25:19.409 --> 00:25:21.150
